oNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">相关卡片：类与对象、构造方法</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:40.9pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:40.9pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">备注：无</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</div>'),(9,'<div class=\"Section1\" style=\"layout-grid:15.6pt\">\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#F2F2F2;border-collapse:collapse\">\n <tbody><tr style=\"height:6.65pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:6.65pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:20.8pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:20.8pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片编号<span lang=\"EN-US\">:3.3</span></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.15pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.15pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片标题：构造方法</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.45pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.45pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片内容：</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:91.4pt\">\n  <td width=\"17\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"536\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:401.8pt;background:white;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（1）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">构造方法的作用与定义</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">在对象被创建时初始化对象的成员的一种特殊方法</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">主要作用：是对类对象的初始化工作</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">在创建一个类的对象的同时，系统会自动调用该类的构造方法为新的对象初始化。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">可带参数，还可以完成赋值之外的其他复杂操作</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">构造方法的方法名与类名相同。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（2）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">默认的构造方法</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">如果省略构造方法，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java</span>编译器会自动为该类生成一个默认的构造方法，程序在创建对象时会自动调用默认的构造方法。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Cylinder(){}</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（3）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">构造方法（函数）的重载</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">构造函数的重载是指同一个类中存在着若干个具有不同参数列表的构造函数</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">让用户用不同的参数来构造初始化对象。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（4）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">从一个构造方法调用另一个构造方法</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">作用：缩短程序代码，减少开发程序时间。 </span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">从某一构造方法内调用另一构造方法，必须通过关键字<span lang=\"EN-US\">this</span>来调用的，否则编译出错。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  this</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">关键字必须写在构造方法内的第一行位置。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（5）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">公共构造方法与私有构造方法</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:31.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">构造方法一般都是<span lang=\"EN-US\">public</span>，因为它们在创建对象时，是在类的外部被系统自动调用的。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:31.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">构造函数若被声明为<span lang=\"EN-US\">private</span>，则无法在构造方法所在的类以外的地方被调用，但在该类的内部还是可以被调用。</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"16\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:11.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">相关卡片：类与对象、方法的重载</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:40.9pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:40.9pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">备注：无</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</div>'),(10,'<div class=\"Section1\" style=\"layout-grid:15.6pt\">\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#F2F2F2;border-collapse:collapse\">\n <tbody><tr style=\"height:6.65pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:6.65pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:20.8pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:20.8pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片编号<span lang=\"EN-US\">: 4.1</span></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.15pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.15pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片标题：类的继承</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.45pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.45pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片内容：</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:91.4pt\">\n  <td width=\"17\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"536\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:401.8pt;background:white;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（1）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">继承的概念</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">当一个类获取另一个类中所有非私有数据和操作的定义作为自己的部分或全部成分时，就称这两个类之间具有继承关系</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（2）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Java</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">子类的创建（派生）</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Java</span><span style=\"font-family:\n  &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">中的继承是通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">extends</span>关键字来实现的，在定义时用<span lang=\"EN-US\">extends</span>关键字指明新定义类的父类（超类），就在两个类之间建立了继承关系</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">class SubClass extends SuperClass {</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">……</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">}</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（3）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">在子类中访问父类的成员</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">super</span>不但可以访问父类的构造方法，还可以访问父类的成员变量和成员方法，但<span lang=\"EN-US\">super</span>不能访问在子类中添加的成员。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">访问父类成员的格式如下：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  super.</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">变量名；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  super.</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">方法名；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（4）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">覆盖</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">覆盖是指在子类中，定义名称、参数个数与类型均与父类完全相同的方法，用以重写父类里同名方法的功能（方法实现体）。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（5）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">不可被继承的成员与最终类</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">最终类：用<span lang=\"EN-US\">final</span>修饰的类。该类不能有子类。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">最终成员：用<span lang=\"EN-US\">final</span>修饰类的成员。修饰后，不能被子类的成员所覆盖。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（6）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Object</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">类 </span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">是<span lang=\"EN-US\">java.lang</span>类库中的一个类；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">如果某个类没有使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">extends</span>指明父类，默认为<span lang=\"EN-US\">java.lang.Object</span>类的子类。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">是所有类的源。</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"16\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:11.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: