对应了某一组功能。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（2）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">接口的语法</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">[public]&nbsp; interface&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">接口名<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;\n  [extends&nbsp; </span>父接口名列表<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">{&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  // </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">接口体 </span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  // </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">常量域声明，蓝色修饰符即使省略，仍然默认为此</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[public] [static] [final]&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">域类型<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>域名<span lang=\"EN-US\"> = </span>常量值；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  // </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">抽象方法声明，蓝色修饰符即使省略，仍然默认为此</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[public] [abstract] </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">返回值 方法名<span lang=\"EN-US\">( </span>参数列表<span lang=\"EN-US\"> )&nbsp; [throw </span>异常列表<span lang=\"EN-US\">];</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">}</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（3）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">接口的实现</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">为接口中的抽象方法书写方法体，称为实现这个接口。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">class&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">类名称<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;\n  implements&nbsp; </span>接口名表</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  {</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  ……</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  }</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（4）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">接口的继承</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Extends</span><span style=\"font-family:\n  &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">：声明该新接口是某个已存在的父接口的派生接口，可继承父接口的所有常量与方法。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:31.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">与类继承的区别：一个接口可以有一个以上的父接口，它们之间用逗号隔开，形成父接口列表。如果接口中定义了与父接口同名的常量或相同的方法，则父接口中的常量被隐藏，方法被覆盖。</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"16\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:11.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">相关卡片：类的继承、继承中方法的覆盖、抽象类、包</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:40.9pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:40.9pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">备注：无</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n