tyle=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">布局管理的定义</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">布局管理即页面管理<span lang=\"EN-US\">(layout)</span>；指窗口上的组件遵循一定的规则来排列，并会随着窗口大小的变化来改变组件大小与位置的一种布局方式。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（2）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">java.awt</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">包中共定义了五种布局管理器分别是：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">流式布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">FlowLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">组件按照加入容器的先后顺序从左向右排列；一行排满后就自动地转到下一行继续从左向右排列；每一行中的组件都居中排列。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">边界式布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">BorderLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">将显示区域按地理方位分为东<span lang=\"EN-US\">(East)</span>、西<span lang=\"EN-US\">(West)</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;\n  </span>南<span lang=\"EN-US\">(South)</span>、北<span lang=\"EN-US\">(North)</span>、中<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Center)</span>五个区域；将组件加入容器中，若没有指定区域，则默认为中间；若将组件加入到已被占用的位置，将会取代原先的组件。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">③<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片式布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">CardLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">把“窗口容器”中的所有组件如同堆叠起来的一付“扑克牌”，每次只能显示最上面的一张一样，这个被显示的组件将占据所有的容器空间；每次仅有一个组件是可见的。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">④<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">网格式布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">GridLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">将容器的空间划分成若干行与列的网格形式，在容器上添加组件时，它们会按从左到右、从上到下的顺序在网格中均匀排列。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">⑤<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">网格包布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">GridBagLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">将容器中的组件按行、列的位置摆放，但各组件所占据的空间可以是互不相同的。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（3）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">Javax.swing</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">包中主要提供了三种布局管理器： </span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">盒式布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">BoxLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">在一行或一列中摆放组件。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">重叠布局管理器<span lang=\"EN-US\">OverlayLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">将加入该容器的所有组件叠放在一起，可将前面组件设为透明的，后面的即能展示。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">③<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">弹簧布局管理<span lang=\"EN-US\">SpringLayout</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">在组件的周围放置一个灵活的弹簧（<span lang=\"EN-US\">spring</span>），这种弹簧可以压缩或伸长，把组件堆放到要求的高度。</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"16\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:11.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">相关卡片：组件和容器、布局管理器</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:40.9pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:40.9pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">备注：无</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</div>'),(25,'<div class=\"WordSection1\" style=\"layout-grid:15.6pt\">\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#F2F2F2;border-collapse:collapse\">\n <tbody><tr style=\"height:6.65pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:6.65pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:20.8pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:20.8pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片编号<span lang=\"EN-US\">:8.4</span></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.15pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.15pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片标题：向窗口添加菜单</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.45pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.45pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片内容：</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:91.4pt\">\n  <td width=\"17\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"536\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:401.8pt;background:white;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（1）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">菜单的定义</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">若干个抽象方法和常量，形成一个属性集合，该属性集合通常对应了某一组功能。可分为弹出式菜单和窗口菜单。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（2）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">在菜单程序设计中通常会用到五种菜单对象：<span lang=\"EN-US\"> JMenuBar</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Jmenu</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenuItem</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\"> JCheckBoxMenuItem</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JRadioButtonMenuItem</span>。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（3）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">菜单的创建：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">首先必须分别创建<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenuBar</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenu</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenuItem</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JCheckBoxMenuItem</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">JRadioButtonMenuItem</span>对象；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">然后用<span lang=\"EN-US\">add()</span>方法把<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenu</span>对象添加到<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenuBar</span>对象中；再把<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenuItem</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">JCheckBoxMenuItem</span>或<span lang=\"EN-US\">JRadioButtonMenuItem</span>对象添加到<span lang=\"EN-US\">JMenu</span>对象中；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">③<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">最后进行事件处理，为相应的菜单项注册对应的事件监听者。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（4）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">窗口菜单：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">窗口菜单是相对于窗口的，它出现在窗口标题栏的下面，总是与窗口同时出现。也不能被布局管理器所控制。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">菜单在菜单中除了上面介绍的菜单项外，还有一种带复选框的菜单项，功能是由<span lang=\"EN-US\">JCheckBoxMenuItem</span>类所实现的。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（5）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">弹出式菜单：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">当在某个组件上单击鼠标右键时，会弹出一个菜单供选择。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">是一种独立的菜单，它附着在某一组件或容器上。程序运行时，一般情况下不显示，只有当用户在附着有弹出式菜单的组件上进行某项操作时才显示，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java</span>语言用<span lang=\"EN-US\">JPopupMenu</span>类实现弹出式菜单的功能。</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"16\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:11.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">相关卡片：容器布局管理器、组件和容器</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:40.9pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:40.9pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">备注：无</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</div>'),(26,'<div class=\"Section1\" style=\"layout-grid:15.6pt\">\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#F2F2F2;border-collapse:collapse\">\n <tbody><tr style=\"height:6.65pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:6.65pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:20.8pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:20.8pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片编号<span lang=\"EN-US\">: 9.1</span></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.15pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.15pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片标题：状态栏</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.45pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.45pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片内容：</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:91.4pt\">\n  <td width=\"17\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"536\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:401.8pt;background:white;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（1）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">状态栏的定义</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">JToolBar</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">，即在工具栏上加一个标签，标签上显示信息，标签是不能改的。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">显示当前所打开窗口或软件的状态。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:7.0pt;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">状态栏的实现</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">JLabel label=new JLabel(\"</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">这里是状态栏<span lang=\"EN-US\">\");</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">toolBar.add(label);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">把标签加到工具栏上</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">contentPane.add(toolBar,BorderLayout.SOUTH);</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:31.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">//</span><span style=\"font-family:\n  &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">把工具栏加到框架的南边</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"16\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:11.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:35.0pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:35.0pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">相关卡片：继承、抽象类</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:40.9pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:40.9pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">备注：无</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</div>'),(27,'<div class=\"WordSection1\" style=\"layout-grid:15.6pt\">\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#F2F2F2;border-collapse:collapse\">\n <tbody><tr style=\"height:6.65pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:6.65pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:20.8pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:20.8pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片编号<span lang=\"EN-US\">:9.2</span></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.15pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.15pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片标题：对话框</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:21.45pt\">\n  <td width=\"568\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:426.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:21.45pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">卡片内容：</span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr style=\"height:91.4pt\">\n  <td width=\"17\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:12.5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"536\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:401.8pt;background:white;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n  height:91.4pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（1）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">对话框的定义</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">对话框是一个临时窗口，用于显示提示信息或者接收用户输入，不能独立存在，是一种可移动窗口。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（2）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">JDialog</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">JDialog</span><span style=\"font-family:\n  &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Swing</span>中提供的用来实现自定义的对话框，<span lang=\"EN-US\"> JDialog</span>类也属于顶层容器，其默认的布局管理器为<span lang=\"EN-US\">BorderLayout</span>。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（3）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">对话框的方式</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:49.5pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">模式对话框：关闭该对话框之前不能访问其他窗口；</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:49.5pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">非模式对话框：在显示时，用户还可以操作其他窗口。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">（4）<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">通过使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">JOptionPane</span>类创建以下四种标准对话框</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">①<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">消息对话框：显示消息，只包含一个“确定”按钮</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">②<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">确认对话框：显示问题，要求用户确认，包含一些可以进行选择的按钮</span></p>\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">③<spa